Delete Your Account
At MS Kongu Matrimony, we respect your privacy and provide an easy way to delete your account. Below are the steps to delete your account using our app.

Steps to Delete Your Account:
Open the App:

Log in to your account using your credentials.
Go to Settings:

Tap on the menu icon (â˜°) or navigate to the Settings section in the app.
Find the "Delete Account" Option:

Scroll down to the Account section and tap Delete Account.
Confirm Deletion:

A confirmation screen will appear. Review the information about account deletion.
Tap Confirm to proceed. Your account will be permanently deleted, and all associated data will be removed from our systems, unless required by law to retain certain information.
